<HEAD>La Junta Man Arrested In Death Threat Case</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LA JUNTA, Colo. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A stockyard worker has been arrested on a
federal warrant for allegedly making a death threat against
presidential candidate Jesse Jackson.
   Leland Duane Bowden, 33, was arrested last Saturday and was able
to post bond Monday after appearing before a U.S. Magistrate,
