<1ST_LINE>r i AM-BRF--SovietBoat     05-20 0109</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-BRF--Soviet Boat,0111</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Soviet Trawler Runs Aground</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Soviet fishing trawler with a crew of 16 ran
aground Friday off the coast of Japan's northern island of
Hokkaido, but no injuries were reported, a Maritime Safety Agency
