<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street Noon,0273</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices were mixed this morning in quiet
trading, which brokers described as a brief pause following the
market's declines earlier this week over fears of higher inflation.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrial stocks was up 1.16 points
to 1,959.88 as of noon EDT. Broader market indices were mixed.
   Gaining issues narrowly led declines on the New York Stock
Exchange, with 652 up, 527 down and 583 unchanged. Volume on the
