<2ND_LINE>PM-Wall Street 3pm,0271</2ND_LINE>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Stock prices were mixed today in quiet trading,
which brokers described as a brief pause following the market's
