plan that would reduce the 14.8 percent stake of its largest
shareholder, takeover strategist Carl Icahn.
   Other blue chips were mixed. IBM fell 1 to 109{, Union Carbide
rose } to 18~, Boeing rose 1] to 50], and Bethlehem Steel fell ] to
18}.
   The NYSE's composite index of all listed issues fell 0.28 to
142.73. On the American Stock Exchange, the market value index fell
0.62 to 291.17.
